7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Kafkai and Marketmuse share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Seo Tools, Api Access. Where Kafkai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Multilingual, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Marketmuse uniquely offers Templates and Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Kafkai holds an overall score of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Marketmuse scores 8/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Kafkai offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $29/mo, compared to Marketmuse's starting price of $149/mo. Marketmuse stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Kafkai requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
